name: Treasurer Ball
tweet: Look for unusual wording or markings, like “prop copy” or “in props we trust”. With multiple bills, ensure different serial numbers on the bottom of each bill. All bills (except $1 & $2) have security thread running from top to bottom. Hold the bill up to a light to confirm legal

name: Treasurer Ball
tweet: We're seeing significant increases in scams & counterfeit money this holiday season. Take the extra few seconds & examine dollar bills that come through your hands. This is time for craft sales, holiday goods, and pop up shops w/cash frequent tender.   https://t.co/T45ACchOH2
